          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">üöó</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Armada Terbaru & Terawat</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Semua mobil dalam kondisi prima, bersih, dan selalu diperiksa rutin untuk keamanan Anda.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">üí∞</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Harga Transparan</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Tidak ada biaya tersembunyi. Semua harga sudah termasuk asuransi dan perlengkapan standar.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">üìç</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Coverage Seluruh Bali</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Melayani pickup dan dropoff di seluruh area Bali termasuk bandara, hotel, dan villa.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">üìû</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Support 24/7</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Tim kami siap membantu kapan saja melalui WhatsApp, telepon, atau email.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <section class="cta-section section-padding">
        <div class="cta-card">
          <div class="cta-content">
            <h2 class="cta-title">Siap Melayani Perjalanan Anda di Bali</h2>
            <p class="cta-description">
              Konsultasikan kebutuhan rental mobil Anda dengan tim profesional kami. Dapatkan penawaran terbaik untuk sewa harian, mingguan, atau bulanan.
            </p>
            
            <div class="cta-info">
              <div class="info-item">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                  <path d="M2 6C2 4.89543 2.89543 4 4 4H16C17.1046 4 18 4.89543 18 6V14C18 15.1046 17.1046 16 16 16H4C2.89543 16 2 15.1046 2 14V6Z" stroke="#0033A0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <path d="M2 6L10 11L18 6" stroke="#0033A0" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
                <span>skywhite@rentcar.com</span>
              </div>
              
              <div class="info-item">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                  <path d="M18 14V16C18 17.1046 17.1046 18 16 18H4C2.89543 18 2 17.1046 2 16V14" stroke="#0033A0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
